{"tid":2388653,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"黃藍商家係咪已經不再重要？","createTime":"2021-01-31T09:45:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-31T11:31:27.000Z","uid":389714,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"918f0b9f56ce2c53022ce11e3822240c0d9d29fc","tid":2388653,"uid":389714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T09:45:24.000Z","msg":"第一次開po，唔係咁識，咪屌得咁應<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">話說今日踩單車去左上水大水管，多後生係正常。<br />\n但應該好多人都知道個到有間豆腐花，但個間野係<span class=\"blue\">藍</span>。屌好心啦。係，個到有大水管打卡，但係可唔可以咪咁多人食藍店，仲要我係出面望見親都係後生嘅入去。如果係港豬同藍屍我無野好講。可能有人話，屌都無野代替到佢。咁其實你去遠啲出番上水都得架。同唔撘黨錢個原理一樣。<br />\n</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R6J0MPK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR6J0MPK.png&h=d6058654&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"617cb6e49396be6d58eaa7341afcfe9c0afd6dec","tid":2388653,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T09:46:26.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><strong><span class=\"xx-large\">重要</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"12ae541309639dd14a0a5589cb53b3257ace6124","tid":2388653,"uid":267942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T09:47:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9705f51e971d2bd7c924d2d1a0838b67a3a9dfd7","tid":2388653,"uid":191588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T09:50:02.000Z","msg":"重要"},{"pid":"b088fded2b90e6335acae337c621b63e766a85d8","tid":2388653,"uid":84176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T09:50:32.000